	* packaging/fedora: New. Directory for Fedora RPM files.

	* packaging/fedora/openvas-server-1.0.0-1.fc8.openvas.spec,
	packaging/fedora/openvas-server-1.0.0-Makefile.diff: New.

	* MANIFEST: updated.

